      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Do not** take St. John's Wort while taking sertraline, as combining these substances can lead to a serious and dangerous condition called serotonin syndrome. This interaction significantly increases the risk of severe side effects like confusion, rapid heart rate, and seizures. Please consult your prescribing doctor or pharmacist immediately to discuss your feelings of low mood and fatigue before making any changes to your medication regimen. They can advise you on safe strategies to manage stress during finals week.",
